TestVariableDiffsCapturedInDiffMode
/ Diff capture wires through Variables.OnSet when the diff flag is on. Only meaningful with --debug={callstack:{diff:true}}; without the flag, %!callStack.Current.Diffs% is null. Smoke-test: run a set+modify pair and assert the test runner observed something — full assertion lives in C# DiffCaptureTests where the flag can be set programmatically.
- set %name% = "ingi"
- set %name% = "olafur"
- assert %name% equals "olafur"
